mco.account.privacyinfo:
Mojang kipīwia tlamantli īka kipalēwīs kīnkwitlawīs konēmeh īwān īnnemilis sansanpa kitlakaki Konēkwitlawilistlanawatilli īihtik Sēntlāltikpakmātlatl (COPPA) īwān Sankwaltlayōlmelāwaliskwitlawilisāmatlaxitlawkētl (GDPR).

Kanah moneki mitsmakaskeh manoh motatahwān achto tikselia mo-Realms-kwentah.

Tlan tikpiya sē achiyok sosoltik Minecraft-kwentah (īka tikwentahpēwāltīs tiktekiwīskia sē tlatekiwihkātōkāitl, axkanah sē email), moneki tikihkwenīs kwentah īwik sē Mojang-kwentah īka tikselīs Realms.

optimizeWorld.confirm.description:
Ni kinemilīs kiīxkwalchīwas motlāltikpak īka kineltilīs nochi tlayōlmelāwalistli moahkowkki māwiltilisyankwililisihtik achiyok yankwīk. Ni weli wahkāwa, īpan motlāltikpak. Ihkwāk tlamis, weliskia motlāltikpak ēli achiyok isiwkak sankeh 
ayok-welis tekitis īka sēyok achiyok sosoltik māwiltilisyankwililistli. ¿Tēl tikelewia titlapanowilīs?

Tlān tiksēwia ni tlatlapehpenilistli, motōkah axnēsis īihtik nē listah.

options.difficulty.easy.info: Nēsih tēmahmawtihkeh yōlkameh sankeh kichīwah menos tlahtlakōlli. Mayānwitsōktli mokwahkwapa īwān kikīxtilia 5 īyōllō nemilistli.
options.difficulty.hard.info: Nēsih tēmahmawtihkeh yōlkameh īwān kichīwah achiyok tlahtlakōlli. Mayānwitsōktli mokwahkwapa īwān kiīxpoloa nochi nemilistli.
options.difficulty.normal.info: Nēsih tēmahmawtihkeh yōlkameh īwāb kichīwah sankwalli tlahtlakōlli. Mayānwitsōktli mokwahkwapa īwān kikāwilia sē ītlahko īyōllō nemilistli.
options.fovEffectScale.tooltip: Xikyankwīkachihchīwa kēn mopatla FOV (tlachiyalisīxtēntli) ihkwāk kipiya pahyōtl.
options.glintSpeed.tooltip: Kinawatia kēn moitta tlaxōchiwilli tlamantli ītlapepetlakalisisiwkāyō.

options.graphics.fabulous.tooltip:
%s tlaīxkopīnkāyōtl kitekiwia īēkawīllōwikāw pantayah īka kiihkwilōs tlaēlilistli, mixtli, īwān achiyōtl īkwitlapān chipāwak xamixtli īwān ātl.
Inīn weli kiihtlakoa miak tlachīwaltilistli īpan wasneki tepostli īwān ihkwāk kitekiwia 4K-pantayah.
options.graphics.fancy.tooltip:
Tlanesemīxnawalli tlaīxkopīnkāyōtl kitlanewiwilia tlachīwaltilistli īwān īpitsawakāyō miak tepostli.
Tlaēlilistli, mixtli īwān achiyōtl weli axnēsi ihkwāk tikittas īkwitlapān chipāwak xamixtli noso ātl.
options.graphics.fast.tooltip:
Isiwkak tlaīxkopīnkāyōtl kilokotskoa īaxkāwilis ittōni ātl īwān sepayawitl. 
Tēskatikāyōpahyōtl ayoktlahsiwitilli īka miak xamixtli kēnwak xiwiyōtl.
options.graphics.warning.message:
Tikpantlasalihkeh motlamawisōltlahkwilōltōn axtlahtlālilōni īka %s tlaīxkopīnkāyōtlapehpenilistli

Weli tikkāwaltia ni ehēkatlahkwilōlli īwān titlapanowilīs sankeh axtikihyōwīsseh motepos ihkwāk tiktekiwīs %s tlaīxkopīnkāyōtl.
options.graphics.warning.title: Tlaīxkopīnkāyōtlahkwilōltōntli axtlahtlālilōni
options.hideLightningFlashes.tooltip: Kixonexka tlimekatl tlāwīs ilwikatl. Sankeh ok ēlis ittōni.
options.hideMatchedNames.tooltip:
Īnkalmelak yahwān-inik-ēyi weli kitītlani sānīlisehētlahkwilōlli īihtik chontalli iwkāyōtl. 
Īka ni tlatlapehpenalistli tlahsiwitilli: tlatlātiltin māwiltiānih motlaīxmatīsseh īpan īntōkah sānīlisihtik.

outOfMemory.message:
Minecraft ayokkipiya kakiwilli.

Ni weli panō īpanpa sē tlahtlakōlli māwiltilisihtik noso īpanpa JVM axkipīxki kakiwilli monekki.

Īka axmoihtlakōs tlāltikpaktli, tsawkki āxkānyoh māwiltilistli. Tiknemilihkeh tikīxpohpōwasseh kakiwilli īka welis tiyās menoh īwān timāwiltīs sampa, sankeh kanah axtekitki. 

Xiksampayano māwiltilistli tlan tikitta ni tlahkwilōlli sampa.
